):

1. *Vera* je začarana reč koja znači vere u sebe i u druge. (Vera is a magical word that means faith in oneself and in others.)

2. Njena *vera* u njegovu ljubav bila je neizmerna. (Her faith in his love was immeasurable.)

3. Kako smo stari, tako nam se i *vera* menja. (As we get older, so does our faith change.)

4. *Verom* postižemo mir i harmoniju u našim životima. (With faith we achieve peace and harmony in our lives.)

5. Neke stvari ne možeš dobiti bez *vere*. (Some things cannot be obtained without faith.)